SERVER CREATION

Basic commands

1.create package.jason = npm init
2.create node modules
  installing express:  npm i express

Basic steps
1.  Creating a folder (bankserver)
2.  create package.jason
3.  create nodemodules
4.  create index.js 
5.  import express inside index.js
6.  create app using express
7.  setup port number
8.  resolving http requests
9.  install nodemon -  npm i -g nodemon
10. http response code
     100 range -- info
     200 range -- success
     300 range -- redirection
     400 range -- client error
     500 range -- server error
11. JWT token authentication
    to check the login activity
    login -----tokengenerated---->client-----req to deposit+token---->server token check?
    i)  install JWT token - jsonwebtoken
        npm i jsonwebtoken
   ii)  to generate a new JWT token - sign()
   iii) middleware - to veriy token
        comes in the middle of the request and response
        it also provide access to many function
        a. Application level middle ware
          for entire Application

