12.  Database integration
        install mongoose - npm i mongoose - for connecting nodejs and mongodb
        db connect via mongoose
        create a model using mongoose

13. Asynchronous function resoling
        resolving state - then()
        rejection state - catch() 

14. CORS - cross origin resource sharing
           instll cors - npm i cors